sequenceDiagram
    participant A as User A
    participant CSA as Chat Server A
    participant Reg as Session Registry
    participant Bus as Message Bus
    participant CSB as Chat Server B
    participant Store as Message Store
    participant Push as Push Notif (APNs/FCM)
    participant B as User B

    A->>CSA: WS send {to:B, body, client_msg_id}
    CSA->>Store: persist message (sync)
    Store-->>CSA: server_msg_id, ts
    CSA-->>A: ack {server_msg_id, ts}
    CSA->>Reg: lookup B's chat server
    alt B online
        Reg-->>CSA: chat_server_B
        CSA->>Bus: publish to recipient topic
        Bus-)CSB: deliver
        CSB->>B: WS receive {from:A, body, server_msg_id}
        B-->>CSB: delivered receipt
        CSB->>Bus: publish receipt
        Bus-)CSA: receipt event
        CSA->>A: WS receipt {state: delivered}
    else B offline
        Reg-->>CSA: not connected
        CSA->>Push: send push notification
        Note over B,Push: B reconnects later, syncs from last_read_msg_id
    end
